    [
      "p",
      null,
      "When a multi-app project is detected, the Ionic CLI will operate under the context of an app configured in the root ",
      [
        "code",
        null,
        "ionic.config.json"
      ],
      ". Project selection criteria is as follows:"
    ],
    " ",
    [
      "ol",
      null,
      " ",
      [
        "li",
        null,
        "If the global CLI option ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "--project"
        ],
        " is specified, the project is looked up by key in the ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "projects"
        ],
        " object. For example, ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "--project=myApp"
        ],
        " will select the ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "myApp"
        ],
        " project."
      ],
      " ",
      [
        "li",
        null,
        "If the CLI detects it is being run within a project path, configured with the ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "root"
        ],
        " key, it will select the matched project. For example, using the CLI within the ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "apps/myOtherApp/src"
        ],
        " directory will select the ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "myOtherApp"
        ],
        " project."
      ],
      " ",
      [
        "li",
        null,
        "If a ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "defaultProject"
        ],
        " is specified in ",
        [
          "code",
          null,
          "ionic.config.json"
        ],
        ", it will select the specified project when the above criteria is not met."
      ],
      " "
